trans-unit.source: The Pkcs9DocumentName class defines the name of a CMS/PKCS #7 message.
trans-unit.target: Klassen Pkcs9DocumentName definerer navnet på en CMS/PKCS #7-melding.

trans-unit.source: The Pkcs9DocumentName constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentName"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren Pkcs9DocumentName oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentName"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The Pkcs9DocumentName constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentName"></xref> class by using the specified array of byte values as the encoded name of the content of a CMS/PKCS #7 message.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren Pkcs9DocumentName oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentName"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av den angitte matrisen byte som kodet navnet på innholdet i en CMS/PKCS #7-melding.

trans-unit.source: An array of byte values that specifies the encoded name of the CMS/PKCS #7 message.
trans-unit.target: En matrise med byteverdier som angir kodet navnet på CMS/PKCS #7-melding.

trans-unit.source: The Pkcs9DocumentName constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentName"></xref> class by using the specified name for the CMS/PKCS #7 message.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren Pkcs9DocumentName oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentName"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av det angitte navnet for CMS/PKCS #7-melding.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> object that specifies the name for the CMS/PKCS #7 message.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>objekt som angir navnet på CMS/PKCS #7-melding.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: This method replaces the current <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentName> object with the specified <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData> object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden erstatter gjeldende <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentName>objekt med angitt <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData"></xref> object from which to copy information.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData"> </xref> objektet vil kopiere informasjon fra.

trans-unit.source: The DocumentName property retrieves the document name.
A <xref:System.String> object that contains the document name.
